ges/posticons/pi_freak.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/29/02 2:36:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4573.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The General Fight</span><hr size=1> I swear I searched through many many threads looking for this info and didn't find it. <br>What kind of forces are needed to take out the General?<br>I read that a good 55ish group can take the DEs around him but what do I need to add to kill the big guy?<br>Thanx! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/urizickkiedis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RIZICK KIEDIS</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/2/02 6:52:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4573.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The General Fight</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://matt.waggoner.com/ragebringer.html">matt.waggoner.com/ragebringer.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ushjekai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shjekai</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_freak.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/5/02 9:33:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4573.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The General Fight</span><hr size=1> Thanks for the link but I have the guide already and nearly memorized at this point. <br>Maybe this is a touchy question but I'm looking for some advice on how to get this guy killed. Like how many people and what kind, levels, classes, what spells stick, how hard does he hit, how many hps. Maybe just post personal experiences with this fight. <br>I have also heard of people losing their Box. How is that possible and how can it be avoided. <br>Thanks.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udaard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/6/02 9:29:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4573.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The General Fight</span><hr size=1> Getting aggroed while turning in the box will cause it to be lost. To avoid that, leave one DE in the corner of the cabin to give it to, and do it during the day, when there are no roaming undead around.<br><br>As far as how to kill him, you just have to do 32k damage to him before he wipes out everyone. If you have a 57+ tank, I recommend maintanking him, and have 1 cleric for CH, and a 2-3 others to patch heal him. For damage, use monks/rogues and nukers with lures and fire nukes. Without a mt, you're gonna have to zerg him. If you do that, get as many riposte tanks as possible, and nuke him from the beginning of the fight.<br><br>Everytime I've done him before, there were 40-60 people on hand for the fight. Even with a lot of people who were 50-55, he went down very quickly. <br><br>If you fail, get someone to kite him without getting summoned, while you res for another attempt. He despawns after a few minutes. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ureztarn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reztarn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/7/02 10:36:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4573.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The General Fight</span><hr size=1> For kiting a wizard with a staff of temperate flux and Jboots will do as the staff draws a LOT of agro but does no damage.  So  you could even get a level 30ish wizard to do this pretty easy.<br><br>Tizla <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=4573.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4573.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=4573.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=4573.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4573.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4573.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td co